{
  "id": "adv_card_mei_09_02",
  "title": "早坂芽衣 2話 みんなのことが大好き",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣、この前書いてもらったアンケートなんだが……\n出来れば書き直してほしいって連絡があったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei‚ about the survey I asked you to fill out before…\nI was contacted and asked if you could rewrite it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.2655247916,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.1568027497
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "そっか……ごめんね～、{user}さん\n芽衣がうまく答えられなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that so… I’m sorry~‚ {user}-san.\nMei couldn’t answer it properly….",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.9666669528,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.9789112728
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "俺の方こそ、うまく伝えられなくてすまない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sorry I couldn’t communicate it to you properly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.9789112728,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "内容は、先方にお任せすることも出来るが\n俺も一緒に考えるから、もう一度挑戦してみないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We can leave the content up to them‚\nbut since I’ll think about it with you‚ why don’t we give it another shot?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.1666669528,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.165101719
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "うん。ありがとう、{user}さん！\n芽衣ね、あれからも恋愛のこと、考えてみてるの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay. Thank you‚ {user}-san!\nMei has been thinking about love since then‚ you know~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.4326756479
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "学校の友達に聞いたりもしたんだけど\n「胸がぎゅーって締め付けられたりする」って言ってた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I also asked my friends at school\nand they said that “It feels like your heart is being squeezed.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.2000002861,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "でも、どういうことだろう。嬉しくって、誰かを\nぎゅ～ってしたい時はあるけど、多分違うんだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But what does that mean? When I’m happy and I want to\nsqueeze someone in a hug… it probably means something else‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.6000002861,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.3406343145
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "言葉で説明するのは難しいが……恋愛ドラマを観て\n感覚を想像したり、勉強してみてもいいかもな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s hard to explain with words… maybe you could try watching\nromantic dramas and imagining the feeling or studying it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.4943513572,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "後は、全体的な方向性だが……芽衣は、「一緒に楽しい\nことをする」っていうのを大事にしていたな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And‚ about the overall direction… you said that it’s important\nto do something fun together‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.5440250467,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 68.6770285927
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "うん。恋愛とは違うかもしれないけど\n芽衣は、一杯遊びたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. It might be different from love‚ but…\nI want to have lots of fun!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.5666669528,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃんや渚ちゃんのゲームをプレイしてた時もね\n芽衣、一緒にお出かけするシーンが大好きだったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Like when Mei was playing Rei-chan and Nagisa-chan's game‚\nshe loved the scene where they went out together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.9000023206,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.2679605647
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "プレイしてる芽衣も楽しい気持ちになって、幸せだった\nから。芽衣も、みんなをそういう気持ちにしてあげたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei was happy because she was enjoying while she was playing it.\nSo‚ I want to make everyone feel that way too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.133335654,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.4656019374
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "あ！　ずーっと夏休みとかでもいいかも！\nそしたら沢山遊べるし！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh! It would be nice if it was summer vacation forever!\nThen I can play a lot!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.3666689873,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣ね、小学校の頃は、夏休みになると田舎の\nおばあちゃんちに行って遊んでたんだ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I was in elementary school‚ I used to go to my grandma's house\nin the countryside during summer vacation to play~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.2616321929,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.0634705388
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "それならゲームの舞台は『田舎の夏休み』なんてどうだ\nここに恋愛の要素を入れないとだが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So how about we set the game in the “Countryside Summer Vacation”?\nWe need to add some romance to it though…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.2666689873,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.0000023206
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "恋愛……あ、そうだ！　じゃあさ、芽衣と一緒に\n恋愛を勉強出来るゲームにするのはどうかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Romance… Ah‚ that’s right! How about a game\nwhere you can study romance with Mei together?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.633335654,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.0531075005
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "恋愛を勉強出来る？　どういうことだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Study romance? What do you mean?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.0531075005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "えっとね、ゲームの中の芽衣も、今の芽衣と一緒で\n恋愛がどういうものなのか分かんないの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ Mei in the game is just like me now.\nShe doesn't know what love is!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.933335654,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.4787084108
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "それで、ゲームの中で芽衣も恋愛のことを勉強して～\n……あれ？　こんがらがってきたよ～！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ Mei in the game will study love too‚ and~\n…Huh? Now I’m getting confused~!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.1666689873,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 147.2712985838
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "つまり、『恋を知らなかったゲームの中の芽衣が\n主人公と一緒に恋を学んでいく』ということか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So you’re saying‚ “Mei in the game‚ who didn’t know about love‚\nwill learn about love with the protagonist”?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.9666740735,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣っぽいストーリーだし、いい案かもしれないな\nその案で先方に提案してみるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s a Mei-like story‚ and it might be a good idea.\nI’ll propose that idea to them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.9390576347,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 161.340658554
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02-mei013.m4a",
      "text": "やったー！　じゃあ、お返事が返ってくるまでに\n芽衣も恋愛について、しっかり勉強しなきゃ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yay~! Then Mei has to study hard about love\nuntil they get back to us!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.5666689873,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 169.0767306494
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02-mei014.m4a",
      "text": "恋愛ドラマを観たり、沢山話を聞いたり！\n{user}さんも、芽衣に一杯教えてね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll watch romantic dramas and hear lots of stories!\n{user}-san‚ you should teach me lots too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.9333305677,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_02-koh010.m4a",
